Introduction

D.COY was a four-member boy band under Rolling Culture One, consisting of members Jungmin, Hyukjin, Wonshin, and Dosun. The group debuted on February 19, 2020, with the single album Color Magic.

Former member Jaehoon left the band in 2019, and Sungwoon departed on February 8, 2021. On February 13, 2023, it was announced that D.COY had disbanded, with the members preparing for a new start.
